**/Backup_*/**/*_00*.cs.meta

# ZIP archives in Assets
Assets/**/*.zip
Assets/**/*.zip.meta

# Recovery & temp Unity folders
Assets/Temp/
Assets/Temp.meta
Assets/_Recovery/
Assets/_Recovery.meta

